  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "chapterTitle": "再谈邓小平和20世纪的中国",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD_15_9923-10023",
          "range": "9923-10023",
          "rangeStart": 9923,
          "rangeEnd": 10023,
          "markText": "周总理曾经问过一个邓小平的部下，你跟了小平那么多年印象最深的是什么？他回答说：果断。小平同志果断并不是说武断，他是从实际出发，一切强调实事求是，在一定时期里中央侧重强调某个方面，但是不能忽略另外一面。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1709767338,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-07 07:22:18",
          "chapterUid": 15,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=9923&rangeEnd=10023",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d0420b3643425f365756327658327476316979366d6d366b65394f6e4644443d7?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=9923&rangeEnd=10023"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD_15_10452-10515",
          "range": "10452-10515",
          "rangeStart": 10452,
          "rangeEnd": 10515,
          "markText": "引用小平同志的那句话，最能体现他的风格：“说话嘛，就是要明确，不能含含糊糊、吞吞吐吐，否则，解决不了问题，动作要快，不能拖。”",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1709767337,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-07 07:22:17",
          "chapterUid": 15,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=10452&rangeEnd=10515",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d0420b3643425f365756327658327476316979366d6d366b65394f6e4644443d7?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=10452&rangeEnd=10515"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD_15_3247-3326",
          "range": "3247-3326",
          "rangeStart": 3247,
          "rangeEnd": 3326,
          "markText": "社会主义初级阶段的基本国情没有变，人民日益增长的物质文化需要同落后的社会生产之间的矛盾这一社会主要矛盾没有变，我国是世界上最大的发展中国家的国际地位没有变。”",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1709767336,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-07 07:22:16",
          "chapterUid": 15,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=3247&rangeEnd=3326",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d0420b3643425f365756327658327476316979366d6d366b65394f6e4644443d7?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=3247&rangeEnd=3326"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "chapterTitle": "刘少奇是善于独立思考的战略家和理论家",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD_11_3334-3436",
          "range": "3334-3436",
          "rangeStart": 3334,
          "rangeEnd": 3436,
          "markText": "“人类社会的历史在客观上总是循着曲折的道路前进的。这是由于历史是在社会矛盾之斗争中发展的这种情形所决定的。虽然人们在主观上常常想推动历史依照客观上可能的直线道路前进，然而客观的历史行程总还是走着弯曲的道路",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1709727042,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-06 20:10:42",
          "chapterUid": 11,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=3334&rangeEnd=3436",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d0420b3643425f365756327658327476316979366d6d366b65394f6e4644443d7?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=3334&rangeEnd=3436"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD_11_6521-6541",
          "range": "6521-6541",
          "rangeStart": 6521,
          "rangeEnd": 6541,
          "markText": "研究刘少奇的革命活动，也需要把视野放宽。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1709727041,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-06 20:10:41",
          "chapterUid": 11,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=6521&rangeEnd=6541",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d0420b3643425f365756327658327476316979366d6d366b65394f6e4644443d7?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=6521&rangeEnd=6541"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD_11_6721-6739",
          "range": "6721-6739",
          "rangeStart": 6721,
          "rangeEnd": 6739,
          "markText": "研究和宣传少奇同志还要和现实相结合。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1709727040,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-06 20:10:40",
          "chapterUid": 11,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=6721&rangeEnd=6739",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d0420b3643425f365756327658327476316979366d6d366b65394f6e4644443d7?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=6721&rangeEnd=6739"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD_11_3112-3217",
          "range": "3112-3217",
          "rangeStart": 3112,
          "rangeEnd": 3217,
          "markText": "这个 绪论里有四点，其中第二点是讲卢沟桥事变以后中国的新形势、党的新任务与革命斗争的新形式；第三点是讲党应该采取哪种形式的抗日武装斗争和哪里是党的主要工作地区；第四点是讲党在抗日民族统一战线问题中行动路线的决定",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1709727039,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-06 20:10:39",
          "chapterUid": 11,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=3112&rangeEnd=3217",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d0420b3643425f365756327658327476316979366d6d366b65394f6e4644443d7?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=3112&rangeEnd=3217"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "chapterTitle": "陈云和学哲学",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD_16_6593-6754",
          "range": "6593-6754",
          "rangeStart": 6593,
          "rangeEnd": 6754,
          "markText": "从实际出发，说起来容易，做起来并不容易。客观事物是复杂的，常常包含相互矛盾的多个侧面，并且在不断发生变化，不是一眼都能看清楚的。人们对事物的认识，通常需要经过一个在实践中由浅入深、由表及里的过程。决不能把走马看花时获得的一点粗枝大叶的印象甚至一些道听途说的靠不住的话当作客观实际的全体，而且还自以为是，那样没有不跌跤子的。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1709727039,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-06 20:10:39",
          "chapterUid": 16,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=6593&rangeEnd=6754",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d0420b3643425f365756327658327476316979366d6d366b65394f6e4644443d7?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=6593&rangeEnd=6754"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "chapterTitle": "毛泽东和周恩来",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD_8_3773-3888",
          "range": "3773-3888",
          "rangeStart": 3773,
          "rangeEnd": 3888,
          "markText": "胡乔木同志讲到过，有一次他劝主席多到工厂去看看。主席说，我怎么去啊？我一去，人都围了上来，是我看工厂，还是工厂看我？在毛泽东晚年这种同实际越来越隔膜的状况下，周恩来在一些方针政策的制定方面对毛泽东所起的补充作用似乎比以往更多一些。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1709724791,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-06 19:33:11",
          "chapterUid": 8,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3773&rangeEnd=3888",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d0420b3643425f365756327658327476316979366d6d366b65394f6e4644443d7?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3773&rangeEnd=3888"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "chapterTitle": "毛泽东工作方法的几个特点",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD_6_3931-3993",
          "range": "3931-3993",
          "rangeStart": 3931,
          "rangeEnd": 3993,
          "markText": "“研究任何过程，如果是存在着两个以上矛盾的复杂过程的话，就要用全力找出它的主要矛盾。捉住了这个主要矛盾，一切问题就迎刃而解了",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1709724787,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-06 19:33:07",
          "chapterUid": 6,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3931&rangeEnd=3993",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d0420b3643425f365756327658327476316979366d6d366b65394f6e4644443d7?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3931&rangeEnd=3993"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD_6_1124-1176",
          "range": "1124-1176",
          "rangeStart": 1124,
          "rangeEnd": 1176,
          "markText": "“拿战略方针去指导战役战术方针，把今天联结到明天，把小的联结到大的，把局部联结到全体，反对走一步看一步。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1709724781,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-06 19:33:01",
          "chapterUid": 6,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1124&rangeEnd=1176",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d0420b3643425f365756327658327476316979366d6d366b65394f6e4644443d7?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1124&rangeEnd=1176"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD_6_2707-2841",
          "range": "2707-2841",
          "rangeStart": 2707,
          "rangeEnd": 2841,
          "markText": "“坐在指挥台上，如果什么也看不见，就不能叫领导。坐在指挥台上，只看见地平线上已经出现的大量的普遍的东西，那是平平常常的，也不能算领导。只有当着还没有出现大量的明显的东西的时候，当桅杆顶刚刚露出的时候，就能看出这是要发展成为大量的普遍的东西，并能掌握住它，这才叫领导。”",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1709724780,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-06 19:33:00",
          "chapterUid": 6,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2707&rangeEnd=2841",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d0420b3643425f365756327658327476316979366d6d366b65394f6e4644443d7?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2707&rangeEnd=2841"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD_6_1185-1315",
          "range": "1185-1315",
          "rangeStart": 1185,
          "rangeEnd": 1315,
          "markText": "人们观察和认识事物，通常只能从一个个局部开始，但决不能停留在这里。只有把各个局部综合起来进行分析，形成整体的观念，并且弄清那些局部在全局中所处的位置以及彼此间的联系，才能正确地指导工作。有些事从局部来看是有利的，但从全局来看是不利的，那就得坚决顶住，不能去做。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1709724779,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-06 19:32:59",
          "chapterUid": 6,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1185&rangeEnd=1315",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d0420b3643425f365756327658327476316979366d6d366b65394f6e4644443d7?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1185&rangeEnd=1315"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD_6_670-816",
          "range": "670-816",
          "rangeStart": 670,
          "rangeEnd": 816,
          "markText": "我们不但要提出任务，而且要解决完成任务的方法问题。我们的任务是过河，但是没有桥或没有船就不能过。不解决桥或船的问题，过河就是一句空话。不解决方法问题，任务也只是瞎说一顿。”他的话讲得很重，却是千真万确的真理：即便提出的任务是正确的，道理讲得也很清楚，如果没有好的工作方法来实行它，也会变成空话",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1709724773,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-06 19:32:53",
          "chapterUid": 6,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=670&rangeEnd=816",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d0420b3643425f365756327658327476316979366d6d366b65394f6e4644443d7?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=670&rangeEnd=816"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD_6_4591-4704",
          "range": "4591-4704",
          "rangeStart": 4591,
          "rangeEnd": 4704,
          "markText": "毛泽东同志谈战争问题时说道：“集中兵力 看来容易，实行颇难。人人皆知以多胜少是最好的办法，然而很多人不能做，相反地每每分散兵力，原因就在于指导者缺乏战略头脑，为复杂的环境所迷惑，因而被环境所支配，失掉自主能力，采取了应付主义。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1709724773,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-06 19:32:53",
          "chapterUid": 6,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4591&rangeEnd=4704",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d0420b3643425f365756327658327476316979366d6d366b65394f6e4644443d7?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4591&rangeEnd=4704"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD_6_6804-6849",
          "range": "6804-6849",
          "rangeStart": 6804,
          "rangeEnd": 6849,
          "markText": "而只是冥思苦索地‘想办法’，‘打主意’。须知这是一定不能想出什么好办法，打出什么好主意的。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1709724772,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-06 19:32:52",
          "chapterUid": 6,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6804&rangeEnd=6849",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d0420b3643425f365756327658327476316979366d6d366b65394f6e4644443d7?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6804&rangeEnd=6849"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "chapterTitle": "周恩来的求真与反对极端主义",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD_9_2860-2947",
          "range": "2860-2947",
          "rangeStart": 2860,
          "rangeEnd": 2947,
          "markText": "的环境总有局限性，要从多方面观察问题；一个人的认识总是有限的，要多听不同的意见，这样才利于综合。事物总是发展的，有进步和落后，有一般和特殊，有真和假，要进行比较，才能看透。”",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1709724786,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-06 19:33:06",
          "chapterUid": 9,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2860&rangeEnd=2947",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d0420b3643425f365756327658327476316979366d6d366b65394f6e4644443d7?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2860&rangeEnd=2947"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "chapterTitle": "毛泽东在三大战略决战中",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD_7_1227-1415",
          "range": "1227-1415",
          "rangeStart": 1227,
          "rangeEnd": 1415,
          "markText": "毛泽东曾着重指出这一点：“我要优势和主动，敌人也要这个，从这点上看，战争就是两军指挥员以军力财力等项物质基础作地盘，互争优势和主动的主观能力的竞赛。竞赛结果，有胜有败，除了客观物质条件的比较外，胜者必由于主观指挥的正确，败者必由于主观指挥的错误。”",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1709724780,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-06 19:33:00",
          "chapterUid": 7,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1227&rangeEnd=1415",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d0420b3643425f365756327658327476316979366d6d366b65394f6e4644443d7?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1227&rangeEnd=1415"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD_7_6678-6848",
          "range": "6678-6848",
          "rangeStart": 6678,
          "rangeEnd": 6848,
          "markText": "“学习战争全局的指导规律，是要用心去想一想才行的。”“指挥全局的人，最要紧的，是把自己的注意力摆在照顾战争的全局上面。主要地是依据情况，照顾部队和兵团的组成问题，照顾两个战役之间的关系问题，照顾各个作战阶段之间的关系问题，照顾我方全部活动和敌方全部活动之间的关系问题，这些都是最吃力的地方，如果丢了这个去忙一些次要的问题，那就难免要吃亏了。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1709724779,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-06 19:32:59",
          "chapterUid": 7,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=6678&rangeEnd=6848",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d0420b3643425f365756327658327476316979366d6d366b65394f6e4644443d7?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=6678&rangeEnd=6848"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD_7_1980-2142",
          "range": "1980-2142",
          "rangeStart": 1980,
          "rangeEnd": 2142,
          "markText": "既然如此，为什么毛泽东会成长为一位出色的军事统帅？他的办法是“从战争中学习战争”。这有两层意思：一是要投身到战争实践中去，否则就谈不上从战争中学习战争；二是要在战争实践中用心去想，不断总结实践中成功的经验和失败的教训，用来校正自己的认识和行动，并且 把战争中遇到的重要问题提到较高的原则性上去思索和解决，这就是研究战略问题。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1709724778,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-06 19:32:58",
          "chapterUid": 7,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1980&rangeEnd=2142",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d0420b3643425f365756327658327476316979366d6d366b65394f6e4644443d7?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1980&rangeEnd=2142"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD_7_4111-4445",
          "range": "4111-4445",
          "rangeStart": 4111,
          "rangeEnd": 4445,
          "markText": "毛泽东历来强调：“一战而胜，再及其余，各个击破，全局因而转成了优势，转成了主动。”[8] 他写道：“第一个战斗，关系非常之大。第一个战斗的胜败给予极大的影响于全局，乃至一直影响到最后的一个战斗。”怎样打好“第一个战斗”？毛泽东归纳了三条原则：“第一，必须打胜。必须敌情、地形、人民等条件，都利于我，不利于敌，确有把握而后动手。否则宁可退让，持重待机。机会总是有的，不可率尔应战”；“第二，初战的计划必须是全战役计划的有机的序幕。没有好的全战役计划，绝不能有真正好的第 一仗”；“第三，还要想到下一战略阶段的文章。”",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1709724774,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-06 19:32:54",
          "chapterUid": 7,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_6WV2vX2tv1iy6mm6ke9OnFDD&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4111&rangeEnd=4445",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0d0420b3643425f365756327658327476316979366d6d366b65394f6e4644443d7?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4111&rangeEnd=4445"
        }
      ]
    }
